     F************** GDGR14 **
     FGDGT13  UF  E                    DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1 100 SRCDTA
     I                                       16  21 PPGM
     I                                       30  39 FILE
      * PARM *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @FILE  10
     C                     PARM           @PPGM   6
      * CHAIN *
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           10        CHAINGDGT13               30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FILE
     C                     MOVEL@FILE     FILE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PPGM
     C                     MOVEL@PPGM     PPGM
     C                     UPDATACLSRC
     C                     END
      * END *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
